Boris is the head writer, as well as a performer and editor, on <a href="http://bit.ly/streamHpresents">UCB Digital sketch team Cardinal Goose</a>, and was a member of <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLvMZxK22whIszZ_khoAj_MsL6vawSM5WO">UCB1</a>. Boris is also part of hip hop improv comedy group <a href="http://northcoastnyc.com/">North Coast</a> which has been featured on MTV, VH1, and headlines festivals and colleges nationwide.

He can be seen playing a re-occurring creep in the Broad City webisodes, in the Amazon Prime show ‘Red Oaks’, and has appeared in and written for videos featured on Comedy Central, Collegehumor, FunnyOrDie, High Times, and UCBcomedy.com.

See him live hosting <a href="https://east.ucbtheatre.com/performance/41534">Impro(VS)tandup</a> every month at UCB, playing with North Coast Friday and Saturday nights at the PIT, co-hosting <a href="https://www.facebook.com/clubcomedynyc?fref=ts">Club Comedy</a> every 1st and 3rd Wednesday at Bunga's Den, and <a href="http://boriskhaykin.com/calendar">wherever else.</a>

&nbsp;

&nbsp;

